# NOTE: /public/build is intentionally NOT ignored (deviates from the
# Laravel default). Production deploys go through Plesk's Git pull-only
# integration with no confirmed Node.js/npm on that server, so the compiled
# Vite output is committed here and rebuilt+recommitted locally on every
# frontend change instead of built server-side. If the server ever gets a
# reliable `npm run build` step, revert to ignoring this and build there.
/public/storage
/storage/*.key
/storage/pail
/vendor

# dompdf's font cache (config/dompdf.php font_dir/font_cache). Regenerated
# automatically the first time a PDF is exported. Also, on this project it
# currently caches a copy of Tahoma (see app/Console/Commands/RegisterPdfThaiFont.php)
# which is a Windows-bundled font and not freely redistributable — must
# never be committed regardless of the "just a cache" reason above.
/storage/fonts
Homestead.json
Homestead.yaml
Thumbs.db
